=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"948\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.37.50-948x1024.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-12398\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.37.50-948x1024.jpeg 948w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.37.50-278x300.jpeg 278w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.37.50-768x829.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.37.50-417x450.jpeg 417w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.37.50.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 948px) 100vw, 948px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29bc57c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"29bc57c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0132bd2 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0132bd2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-928c12d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"928c12d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary<\/h3>\n<p><b>Morning Departure:<br><\/b>At 7:30 AM, our driver will pick you up from your riad or hotel in Marrakech. You&#8217;ll travel through the scenic High Atlas Mountains, crossing the famous Tizi n&#8217;Tichka Pass, which offers breathtaking views and opportunities for photos along the way.<\/p>\n<p><b>Visit Ait Ben Haddou:<br><\/b>Arrive at Ait Ben Haddou, a centuries-old village known for its striking red mud-brick architecture. Your guide will take you on a tour through the narrow alleys and impressive kasbahs, sharing stories of its rich history and cultural importance. Ait Ben Haddou has been the backdrop for many famous films, including Gladiator and Game of Thrones.<\/p>\n<p><b>Lunch Break:<br><\/b>Enjoy lunch at a local restaurant near the ksar, savoring traditional Moroccan dishes while soaking in the views of this remarkable site.<\/p>\n<p><b>Explore the Area:<br><\/b>Take some free time to wander the village, meet locals, or simply admire the stunning landscapes that surround Ait Ben Haddou.<\/p>\n<p><b>Return to Marrakech:<br><\/b>In the afternoon, the driver will take you back to Marrakech, retracing the beautiful mountain roads. You&#8217;ll arrive in the early evening, concluding your memorable day trip.<\/p>\n<p><b>Highlights:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Discover the High Atlas Mountains and Tizi n&#8217;Tichka Pass.<\/p>\n<p>Explore the iconic Ait Ben Haddou, a UNESCO World Heritage site.<\/p>\n<p>Enjoy traditional Moroccan cuisine at a local restaurant.<\/p>\n<p>Learn about the area&#8217;s history and culture with a knowledgeable guide.<\/p>\n<p>This one-day trip offers a perfect blend of history, culture, and scenic beauty, making it a must-visit destination during your stay in Marrakech.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u200bfrom Marrakech to Ait Ben Haddou Embark on a fascinating one-day journey from Marrakech to the UNESCO World Heritage site of Ait Ben Haddou, a historic ksar (fortified village) famous for its stunning architecture and cultural significance. Itinerary Morning Departure:At 7:30 AM, our driver will pick you up from your riad or hotel in Marrakech. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11313,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11675","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11675","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11675"}],"version-history":[{"count":26,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11675\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12782,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11675\/revisions\/12782"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11313"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11675"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}